lyrics:
[Verse]
In the land of Vrindavan, a love story was born
Krishna and Radha, their hearts forever torn
They danced in moonlight, their souls entwined
A divine connection, a love so kind

[Chorus]
Krishna and Radha, dancing hand in hand
Their love like a river, flowing across the land
Their feet moved in rhythm, their hearts beat as one
In the ecstasy of love, their union was begun
